 his father was off in the guard. Paige likes a good challenge, especially intellectual ones and even though he&#039;s an earthpony, he&#039;s not terribly strong but he can pull a decent weight. Since he&#039;s traveled most of Equestria, he&#039;s a well-prepared traveller when it comes to going anywhere and often goes on small expeditions for rare and strange items. These expeditions fuel his imagination for his book that he wishes to complete but has been working on for a very long time. Paige is often shy when meeting new ponies but once he warms up to them, he&#039;s a loyal and close friend who&#039;s more than willing to do what it takes to make them feel happy. Paige is oftentimes reckless, however, and denies his own health which has lead him in a lot of bad situations. His heart is of good intent but he inevitably screws things up for himself and makes things worse. He&#039;s quick to forgive and forget if someone has wronged him simply because he aims to others to be happy. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378156985";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781569859";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53793;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53793";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"6";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"224";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:4:"text";s:127:"Also, Paige discovered his talent when he would stay up and tell stories to his younger brother to help them pass the time by. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157013";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781570137";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53798;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53798";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"6";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"224";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"VincentShadow";s:4:"text";s:34:"Thank you. It&#039;s nice to hear.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157205";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781572058";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53802;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53802";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:30:"tell me more about his talent.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157459";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781574591";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53805;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53805";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"6";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"224";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:4:"text";s:163:"Paige&#039;s talent is similar to a bard&#039;s talent; able to take experiences and events and translate them to stories, fables or songs with incredible imagery.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157570";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781575701";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53808;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53808";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:196:"ok. so less specifically writing, as a specifically literary medium, but more the art of the storyteller, with imagery and emotion. not necessarily a writer, though he can be, but a bard at heart.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157613";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781576134";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53809;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53809";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:123:"hmm. ok, i&#039;ll let that percolate. i already have a few small ideas swimming about, but they&#039;ve yet to fully form.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157650";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781576503";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53810;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53810";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"6";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"224";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:4:"text";s:30:"Thanks for helping out, Shard.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157670";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781576707";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53812;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53812";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:679:"first idea, hot off the brainpan, with hardly any refinement. it&#039;s crude and unsubtle, and still a bit cliche. an open book, perhaps a bit off kilter just so it isnt all straight and level, one page showing an image, the other having text.. the image can be evocative of a sunset/rise over a mountain peak on a beach shore. representative of not only his talent in writing, but specifically his use of imagery. IF you can get great enough detail, perhaps the image can be spread across both pages, but be hidden in the negative space of the text. like you put squiggly textlines in ordered lines, but there are breaks (spaces) and the breaks form an image in negative space.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157830";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781578309";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53813;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53813";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:229:"another idea i had just now would be an open book, with a worn and folded map laying atop it off center, akin to an adventure or treasure map, with a nauticle four-point star in a corner of the map to make it feel more adventury.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157873";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781578735";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53815;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53815";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:2:"12";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:143:"that would tie in to his love of adventure and travel, obviously, and that he draws upon this as inspiration for the imagery in his literature.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157896";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781578967";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53816;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53816";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"6";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"224";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:4:"text";s:28:"The second idea sounds nice.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378157950";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781579502";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53818;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53818";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:635:"i actually, personally, like your current mark, the quill and signature, as its simple, and yet provocative. cutiemarks arent usually ultra elaborate and i feel sometimes people go overboard with them, and these ideas are all grandiose.. however one modification of your current mark could be that the quill, instead of coming off of a signature, could be trailing after a simple drawing of something adventurous. the afore mentioned shoreside mountain peak for instance. but it would be interesting in that the image would just be a single unbroken line, rather than a full color cel shaded image with a black line sticking off of it.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378158072";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781580725";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53828;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53828";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"6";s:6:"handle";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"224";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:4:"text";s:145:"I see what you mean. I don&#039;t want to overcomplicate it though ... I wouldn&#039;t have any idea of what the quill could be drawing off from.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378158489";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#42eab2";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781584890";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#b2e8dd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53829;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53829";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:76:"aomething that is imaginitive, and evokes the idea of adventure and imagery.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378158524";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781585247";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:53830;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"53830";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:13:"Crystal_Shard";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"184";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:39:"though that is a very abstract concept.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378158532";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#bfdee0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13781585323";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#d8cafb";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:56530;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"56530";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:4:"boo!";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378348492";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13783484925";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:56531;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"56531";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"2";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"38";s:6:"handle";s:9:"StarOcean";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"223";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:14:"hehe, wassups?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378348499";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#ffa100";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13783484990";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ff7400";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:56662;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:5:"56662";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Fluttershy";s:12:"character_id";s:2:"91";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:17:"Lyra_Heartstrings";s:4:"text";s:9:"/me snugs";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1378352609";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#f281ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13783526092";s:15:"chat_text_color";s